title: 09/28/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 09/28/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's matchup between the Cowboys and Eagles. Is Dallas going to steam roll through the NFC East this season? NBC's Chris Simms joins us to discuss Rookie QBs and playing for bad teams. And Chargers Head Coach Brandon Staley calls in and explains what was the game plan in beating the Chiefs last week.
